<%- include('../partials/head', { lang, t, alternates }) %>
<%- include('../partials/navbar', { lang, t }) %>

<section class="pt-28 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-center mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-400 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: July 1, 2026</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">1. What Data We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">When you create an account or use our services, we collect the following personal data:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 mt-2">
      <li><strong>Username</strong> — used to identify you publicly on the platform</li>
      <li><strong>Email address</strong> — used for account verification, password reset, and communication</li>
      <li><strong>Password hash</strong> — stored as a bcrypt hash; we never store plain-text passwords</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — package publish history, download counts, and page interactions necessary for platform operation</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We use your data exclusively for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 mt-2">
      <li>Account creation and management</li>
      <li>Package publishing and registry functionality</li>
      <li>Sending essential communications (password reset, verification emails)</li>
      <li>Platform security and abuse prevention</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">3. Legal Basis (LGPD Art. 7)</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We process your personal data under the following legal bases as defined by the Brazilian General Data Protection Law (LGPD):</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 mt-2">
      <li><strong>Consent (Art. 7, I)</strong> — you explicitly agree to our privacy policy when creating an account</li>
      <li><strong>Legitimate Interest (Art. 7, IX)</strong> — platform security, fraud prevention, and service improvement</li>
      <li><strong>Legal Obligation (Art. 7, II)</strong> — compliance with applicable laws and regulatory requirements</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We <strong>do not</strong> share, sell, rent, or trade your personal data with third parties. Your data remains exclusively under our control and is only accessed by authorized personnel for the purposes described in this policy.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We retain your personal data for as long as your account remains active. Upon receiving a deletion request, your data is anonymized immediately and fully deleted within 30 days, in accordance with LGPD Art. 15.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">6. Your Rights (LGPD Art. 18)</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">As a data subject, you have the following rights under the LGPD:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 mt-2">
      <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of your personal data at any time</li>
      <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — correct inaccurate or incomplete data</li>
      <li><strong>Deletion</strong> — request the deletion of your account and associated data</li>
      <li><strong>Portability</strong> — export your data in a structured, machine-readable format</li>
      <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> — revoke your consent to data processing at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at the email below.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your personal data, please contact our Data Protection Officer:</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@esc-tech.com.br" class="text-pinky-400 hover:underline">hello@esc-tech.com.br</a></p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">8. Cookie Usage</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We use only <strong>essential cookies</strong> required for the functioning of our platform. Specifically, we use a JWT-based authentication token stored in localStorage (not a cookie). No tracking, analytics, or advertising cookies are used. No third-party cookies are set.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 mt-10 mb-3">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via email or platform notice. Continued use of the platform after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-12 text-center">Last updated: July 1, 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

